 object._selfв†“вЌЁв†ђ2Г—'#.'в‰Ў2в†‘object._self вЌќ Make sure that _self doesn't have a leading '#.' on it
 :If 0 2в‰Ўв‰ўВЁobject вЋ•VGET('_pix_size'вЌ¬)('_extent'вЌ¬) вЌќ Compute pixel-size if not predefined (usually only needed for fixed-position controls)
     marginsв†ђ+/2 2вЌґ+вЊї(##.Classes._supp.GetBorders object)[1;,2;] вЌќ Differences between 'extent' and 'size' (in pixels)
     object._pix_sizeв†ђвЊЉ0.5+margins-вЌЁobject._extentГ—вЉѓ##.Classes._supp.MyUnits parent вЌќ Calculate absolute size (in pixels)
