         {}object._self ##.в€†WI action вЌќ Call в€†WI to do the work, but we can never use a returned result from these operations
     :EndFor

     вЌќ Activate/show the new object as requested
вЌќ? This will have problems on the Printer object -- what do we do about that?
     object._openedв†ђ1 вЌќ It will end up opened after completion, unless 'Close' turns it off below
     :For action :In finalв€©вЌЁacts,(~в€Ё/finalв€Љacts)/ВЇ1в†‘final вЌќ There should usually only be one of these at most; default=Open
вЌќ? This will still work for 'def', won't it?
         aargв†ђ1в†“(actsвЌівЉ‚action)вЉѓarg,вЉ‚вЌ¬
         v0в†ђ-object._classвЉ‚вЌ›в€Љ'Form' 'MDIForm' 'Menu' вЌќ "Invisible" setting for this class
         :Select action
         :Case 'Close'
