             :If parentв‰Ў##.GUIroot
             :OrIf в€§/parent.(_visible _opened)>0 вЌќ Only if the parent object is already being shown
                 object._visibleв†ђ0 вЌќ Pretend that it's not shown yet so we can call the standard routine
                 object('Show'##.Invoke)aarg вЌќ Use its normal Show method which includes firing events
             :EndIf
         :Case 'Open' вЌќ Or none of the above
             object._openedв†ђparent вЋ•VGETвЉ‚'_opened' 1 вЌќ Inherit the parent's opened status to start it off with the right assumption
             :If parentв‰Ў##.GUIroot
